+.RE
+.PP
+\fB\-\-children\-max=\fR
+.RS 4
+Limit the number of events executed in parallel\&.
+.RE
+.PP
+\fB\-\-exec\-delay=\fR
+.RS 4
+Delay the execution of RUN intruction by the given number of seconds\&. This option might be useful when debugging system crashes during coldplug caused by loading non\-working kernel modules\&.
+.RE
+.PP
